In [4]:
def interpol(x1, y1, z1, N):
    '''
    x1, y1: x-y grid coord of the simulation
    z1: the simulation data to interpolate
    N: number of points for plotting/interpolation
    '''
    x1i = np.linspace(x1.min(), x1.max(), N)
    y1i = np.linspace(y1.min(), y1.max(), N)
    z1i = scipy.interpolate.griddata((x1, y1), 
                                        z1, (x1i[None,:], 
                                        y1i[:,None]),
                                        method='linear')
    return x1i, y1i, z1i

principle_axes = {}
for it in iterations:
    rho_xy_1d_level, x1d, y1d = cactus_hdf5_get_level_data(
        f'{root_dir}/output-000{num_dir_plot}/illinoisgrmhd-grmhd_primitives_allbutbi.xy.h5', 
        'ILLINOISGRMHD::rho_b', it, 4)
    xi, yi = np.meshgrid(np.arange(rho_xy_1d_level.shape[0]), np.arange(rho_xy_1d_level.shape[1]), 
                       sparse=False, indexing='xy')
    Qxx = np.sum(rho_xy_1d_level[xi, yi] * (3*x1d[xi]**2 - (x1d[xi]**2 + y1d[yi]**2)) * dx * dy)
    Qyy = np.sum(rho_xy_1d_level[xi, yi] * (3*y1d[yi]**2 - (x1d[xi]**2 + y1d[yi]**2)) * dx * dy)
    Qxy = np.sum(rho_xy_1d_level[xi, yi] * (3*x1d[xi] * y1d[yi]) * dx * dy)
#     for i in range(len(x1d)):
#         for j in range(len(y1d)):
#             Qxx += rho_xy_1d_level[i, j] \
#                     * (3*x1d[i]**2 - (x1d[i]**2 + y1d[j]**2)) \
#                     * dx * dy
#             Qyy += rho_xy_1d_level[i, j] \
#                     * (3*y1d[j]**2 - (x1d[i]**2 + y1d[j]**2)) \
#                     * dx * dy 
#             Qxy += rho_xy_1d_level[i, j] \
#                     * (3*x1d[i] * y1d[j]) \
#                     * dx * dy
    Qmat = np.array([[Qxx, Qxy], 
                [Qxy, Qyy]])
    w, v = np.linalg.eig(Qmat)
    v = v.T
    principle_axes[it] = v

print("plotting density x axis")
fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(20.0, 8.0))
interpolate_1d=True
for it in iterations:
    if interpolate_1d:
        rho_xy_1d, x1d, y1d = cactus_hdf5_get_level_data(
                f'{root_dir}/output-000{num_dir_plot}/illinoisgrmhd-grmhd_primitives_allbutbi.xy.h5', 'ILLINOISGRMHD::rho_b', it, 0)
        inter_rho_xy_plane = scipy.interpolate.interp2d(x1d, y1d, rho_xy_1d, kind='cubic')
        lin = np.linspace(-1.2 * Req, 1.2 * Req, 1000)
        inter_rho_x_axis = inter_rho_xy_plane(principle_axes[it][0, 0] * lin, principle_axes[it][1, 0] * lin)
        ax[0].plot(lin / Req, inter_rho_x_axis[int(inter_rho_x_axis.shape[0]/2), :] / RHO0,
                label=fr't={times[it]/t_P:.3g} $t_P$')
        inter_rho_y_axis = inter_rho_xy_plane(principle_axes[it][0, 1] * lin, principle_axes[it][1, 1] * lin)
        ax[1].plot(lin / Req, inter_rho_y_axis[:, int(inter_rho_y_axis.shape[1]/2)] / RHO0,
                label=fr't={times[it]/t_P:.3g} $t_P$')
    else:
        rho_x_1d = cactus_hdf5_get_1d_data(
            f'{root_dir}/output-000{num_dir_plot}/illinoisgrmhd-grmhd_primitives_allbutbi.x.h5',  'ILLINOISGRMHD::rho_b', it)
        rho_y_1d = cactus_hdf5_get_1d_data(
            f'{root_dir}/output-000{num_dir_plot}/illinoisgrmhd-grmhd_primitives_allbutbi.y.h5',  'ILLINOISGRMHD::rho_b', it)
        ax[0].plot(rho_x_1d[:, 0] / Req, rho_x_1d[:, 1] / RHO0,
                label=fr't={times[it]/t_P:.3g} $t_P$')
        ax[1].plot(rho_y_1d[:, 0] / Req, rho_y_1d[:, 1] / RHO0,
                label=fr't={times[it]/t_P:.3g} $t_P$')
ax[0].set_xlabel(r"$x /R_x$")
ax[0].set_ylabel(r"$\rho_x / \rho_{c,t=0}$")
ax[0].set_xlim([-1.2, 1.2])
ax[0].set_ylim([0, 1.2])
ax[0].legend(loc='upper right')

# get quiver plot using unstructured interpolation of all data (slow)
print("plotting velocity xy")
fig, ax = plt.subplots(1, 2, figsize=(20.0, 8.0))
velx_in_xy_plane = cactus_hdf5_get_2d_data(
    f'{root_dir}/output-000{num_dir_plot}/illinoisgrmhd-grmhd_primitives_allbutbi.xy.h5', 
    'ILLINOISGRMHD::vx', iteration_init)
vely_in_xy_plane = cactus_hdf5_get_2d_data(
    f'{root_dir}/output-000{num_dir_plot}/illinoisgrmhd-grmhd_primitives_allbutbi.xy.h5', 
    'ILLINOISGRMHD::vy', iteration_init)
# get a uniform grid
x1d = numpy.linspace(-1.2, 1.2, 20, endpoint=True)
y1d = numpy.linspace(-1.2, 1.2, 20, endpoint=True)
x, y = numpy.meshgrid(x1d, y1d, indexing='xy')
# interpolate onto grid
u = scipy.interpolate.griddata(
    (velx_in_xy_plane[:, 0]/Req, velx_in_xy_plane[:, 1]/Req), velx_in_xy_plane[:, 2], (x, y))
v = scipy.interpolate.griddata(
    (vely_in_xy_plane[:, 0]/Req, vely_in_xy_plane[:, 1]/Req), vely_in_xy_plane[:, 2], (x, y))
ax[0].scatter(rho_in_xy_plane_init[:, 0] / Req, rho_in_xy_plane_init[:, 1] / Req,
                            c=numpy.log(rho_in_xy_plane_init[:, 2] / RHO0), 
                            label=fr"$\rho_0/\rho_0(c,t=0)$ at time={times[iteration_init] / t_P:.3g} t_P",
                            vmin=-4)
ax[0].quiver(x, y, u, v, label="t=%.3g" % (times[iteration_init] / t_P))
ax[0].set_aspect('equal')
ax[0].set_xlim(-1.2, 1.2)
ax[0].set_ylim(-1.2, 1.2)
ax[0].set_title("3-velocity in xy plane")
ax[0].set_xlabel("x [M]")
ax[0].set_ylabel("y [M]")
ax[0].legend(loc='upper right')
